cs.PL, cs.OS, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.DC

The paper discusses the implementation of a functional package manager and operating system orchestration in Scheme, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and operating systems (cs.OS). The paper also discusses the use of domain-specific languages (DSL) and code reuse, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of gexps, which is a novel way of covering many aspects of OS configuration in a single language, and this falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
